    - 10,000
    - 20,000
    - 50,000
    correctIndex: 2
  - questionID: Gas apa yang dilepaskan paru-paru ke udara?
    questionEN: Which gas do the lungs release into the air?
    answersID:
    - Oksigen
    - Nitrogen
    - Karbon dioksida
    - Hidrogen
    answersEN:
    - Oxygen
    - Nitrogen
    - Carbon dioxide
